  "3294630": {
    "name": "Mini Racer Car Shop Simulator",
    "steam_appid": 3294630,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mini Racer Car Shop Simulator让您管理迷你赛车商店的每个方面！销售精致的迷你汽车和各种备件，提供稀有物品的抽奖，并展示您定制的迷你汽车供顾客购买。随着业务的增长，您可以在赛道上试驾您的作品，评估您的定制迷你汽车，并将您的商店打造成汽车爱好者的首选目的地！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>寻找稀有备件</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了增添额外的刺激，每个汽车包都具有扭蛋系统，您可以试试运气获取稀有备件。每次抽奖提供一个随机部件，可能是完成终极迷你汽车所需的重要部分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294630/extras/03b438047e6b5ecb6c1853fab95be04e.poster.avif?t=1765877715\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294630/extras/03b438047e6b5ecb6c1853fab95be04e.webm?t=1765877715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294630/extras/03b438047e6b5ecb6c1853fab95be04e.mp4?t=1765877715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>销售迷你汽车</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您将可以访问各种微型赛车模型，所有这些模型都以令人印象深刻的细节制作，以吸引汽车爱好者。您需要仔细管理库存，以确保始终提供最佳选择，让顾客满意，并使业务蓬勃发展。作为店主，您还可以通过打开汽车包拥有自己的迷你汽车收藏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294630/extras/75e20101ac22163e4bd79e53cbb4c0b5.poster.avif?t=1765877715\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294630/extras/75e20101ac22163e4bd79e53cbb4c0b5.webm?t=1765877715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294630/extras/75e20101ac22163e4bd79e53cbb4c0b5.mp4?t=1765877715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>销售备件</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您不仅销售微型汽车，还可以提供各种备件以提升迷你汽车的性能。从迷你发动机到车轮和独特的备件，为您的顾客提供最佳选择，以打造他们梦想的迷你汽车。每个部件都有不同的质量等级和性能，因此您需要在库存和提供最佳服务方面具有战略眼光，确保忠实客户的满意。您还可以抓取一个包来改装自己的汽车。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294630/extras/13eca0cd0591e7d65f344ee9f59b331e.poster.avif?t=1765877715\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294630/extras/13eca0cd0591e7d65f344ee9f59b331e.webm?t=1765877715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294630/extras/13eca0cd0591e7d65f344ee9f59b331e.mp4?t=1765877715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>定制汽车展示</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在引人注目的展示区展示您的最佳作品！在这里，您可以展示您最令人印象深刻的定制迷你汽车供顾客购买。对于每个杰作，您可以根据汽车性能自行定价。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294630/extras/bda74f78c5e534027d1cb5858c850b4d.poster.avif?t=1765877715\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294630/extras/bda74f78c5e534027d1cb5858c850b4d.webm?t=1765877715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294630/extras/bda74f78c5e534027d1cb5858c850b4d.mp4?t=1765877715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>试驾您的汽车</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在赛道上体验试驾您定制的迷你汽车！此功能可让您亲身感受定制汽车的性能。无论是测试速度、操控，还是独特的升级，赛道都提供了一个令人兴奋的方式来展示您的定制迷你汽车的质量和能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294630/extras/81f879f1a9cfc9707e7c9e5a967e4842.poster.avif?t=1765877715\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294630/extras/81f879f1a9cfc9707e7c9e5a967e4842.webm?t=1765877715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294630/extras/81f879f1a9cfc9707e7c9e5a967e4842.mp4?t=1765877715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mini Racer Car Shop Simulator提供创意，使其成为迷你汽车爱好者的理想天堂。立即开始，将您的商店转变为顾客的终极目的地！</p>",
